Package: apt-changelog-viewer
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0
Description: GTK4 changelog viewer for installed packages with security alerts
 apt-changelog-viewer displays changelogs for installed Debian/Ubuntu
 packages in a modern GTK4 interface. It highlights security updates
 and provides an easy way to review package changes.
